data.description: Updated appliances including washer and dryer! A couple minutes from I-26 right by Nexton! Brand new Roof replaced in 2020! New HVAC unit being installed 09/12/2020. Hot tub, 6-camera security system and pool table convey. Front of the house has the 3 bedrooms including the master with it's own bathroom, back of the house is perfect for entertaining guests! Backyard includes Gazebo and shed with electricity. Fully fenced in. Living room includes wood burning fireplace NO HOA and in a X-flood zone! (no flood insurance required)
